BitstringSearch version 0.03
======================

BitstringSearch is a text document indexer for fast word searches.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DB_File
  Fcntl

